{"tid":1246111,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"快入，美國白宮簽名，Please Liberate Hong Kong，填幾隻字，盡一分力","createTime":"2019-06-20T14:41:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T10:23:21.000Z","uid":42050,"like":49,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"5fb50c3854f0e0027980c5df6b0a986d9a7f44eb","tid":1246111,"uid":42050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T14:41:57.000Z","msg":"個係美國白宮簽名網站，希望大家得閒簽個名（簽完入Email確認)，喺G20國際峰會前(6月28日)促請特朗普關注事件<br />\n<br />\n陳雲：香港是否得救，是否被林鄭秋後算帳，靠白宮聯署及G20請願。<br />\n白宮聯署是打響頭炮，簽名數字不要低得難看啊！<br />\n（香港人是政治巫術高手。他們認為一定要五六個鐘頭滴汗遊行才是努力做嘢，而舉手之勞向特朗普總統請願不是做嘢。故此簽名數目低，是正常的。人蠢，預咗。）<br />\n（簽名呼籲的內文是朋友照搬我建議香港人在大阪高峰會給記者詢問的時候的簡單特朗普式口頭英文，沒有重寫。）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/president-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation?fbclid=IwAR0eD7ytTjSwdRl9nMEybLp6Xr5bFVg0qDkq5-YrdhsVKvQ8XvSZL5BW9iU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fpresident-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0eD7ytTjSwdRl9nMEybLp6Xr5bFVg0qDkq5-YrdhsVKvQ8XvSZL5BW9iU&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4rankPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=3c26f510\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/president-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation?fbclid=IwAR0eD7ytTjSwdRl9nMEybLp6Xr5bFVg0qDkq5-YrdhsVKvQ8XvSZL5BW9iU</a>"},{"pid":"250cde6c35961d32d263b670a880b6cc570fdc54","tid":1246111,"uid":42050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T14:42:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9695f4c03c07c4943caad4b53a0d88b9db9e45ce","tid":1246111,"uid":42050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T14:42:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c126425fe589acd06d712e82422508b07d10f2","tid":1246111,"uid":212626,"like"