<br />\n15.前上司何志平為中共石油供應搭路而貪污非洲國家，年前於美國被捕<br />\n16.陳雲於政府任職時推出於晚間新聞前播放中共國歌，以強化年輕人的愛國思想"},{"pid":"a1978f1e9a0bdb0b7575824990866783099216db","tid":1246111,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T09:07:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"42aa55676f3d171fc1652dfbcbb393b798dd52d8","tid":1246111,"uid":221927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T09:10:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5901c6a459847a5a655fedcf8b311d44608e5e89","tid":1246111,"uid":265556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T09:12:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fe0344925056bd52c7b9baea55093aa85a0019f1","tid":1246111,"uid":249526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T09:41:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06662ee013555c03f13193b6ff33e313b64d913a","tid":1246111,"uid":42050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T09:51:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5272873635ddf3510ecca3b758c6db5db7aa60c1","tid":1246111,"uid":260588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T09:51:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e22959d49dfd0f4cf99bbb992d0151c80b5e3897","tid":1246111,"uid":50268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T09:51:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb013995bea9af65510953f06ee557cfcec6a782","tid":1246111,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T09:52:09.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}